<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">PE（市盈率）知识库</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">用“盈利”来定价的核心指标之一。更适合利润稳定/可持续的行业，强周期与一次性利润占比高的行业需谨慎解读。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">
            <a href="/kb" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">知识库</a>
            <span class="text-gray-300 mx-2">/</span>
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">股票列表</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. PE 是什么？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>PE（Price-to-Earnings）= 股价 / 每股收益（EPS），或市值 / 净利润。直观含义：市场愿意用多少年的“当前盈利”来买这家公司。</p>
            <p>PE 的核心前提是：盈利要足够“可持续、可预测、可重复”。一旦盈利是周期性、一次性、或会计口径波动较大，PE 的指示意义会明显下降。</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. PE(TTM) 常见坑</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">周期顶部“低PE”</div>
                <div>周期股在高景气时利润暴增，TTM 盈利被抬高，PE 看起来很低，但风险可能正在上升。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">一次性收益“美化PE”</div>
                <div>资产处置、补贴、投资收益等会推高利润，TTM PE 可能短期失真。需要回到主营盈利与现金流。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. 历史分位（PE Percentile）怎么用？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>历史分位回答“当前 PE 在过去一段时间（例如近 10 年）处于什么位置”。它是同一标的的自我比较工具。</p>
            <p>更适合用于分档和再平衡：低分位代表估值相对更便宜，高分位代表市场预期更乐观、容错率更低。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800">低估</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">0% - 30%</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800">正常</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">30% - 70%</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800">高估</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">70% - 100%</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. 本系统里的 PE 等级（PE Level）</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">基于当前 PE(TTM) 的绝对区间，便于快速粗筛：</div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">亏损</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(PE &lt; 0)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">极低估</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(0 - 10)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">低估</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(10 - 20)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">合理</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(20 - 30)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">偏高</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(30 - 50)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">高估</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(50 - 100)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3 md:col-span-2"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">极高估</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(PE &gt; 100)</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">使用建议</div>
            <div>PE Level 适合快速筛选，PE 分位更适合对同一标的做“相对便宜/相对贵”的判断。对强周期行业，建议优先结合景气位置与盈利质量。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
        <div>提示：以上内容仅用于解释指标与方法论，不构成任何投资建议。市场有风险，决策需自担。</div>
    </section>
</div>

